{"tid":2366145,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"Razer《雷蛇》 發表口罩中的「機皇」！ 採用 N95 規格搭配 RGB 燈效、麥克風、揚聲器","createTime":"2021-01-14T09:24:32.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-14T10:50:35.000Z","uid":104138,"like":17,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"3ab7c29e9db1a98213e705b90508bd7836586bdb","tid":2366145,"uid":104138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-14T09:24:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn2.techbang.com/system/excerpt_images/83780/post_inpage/9fd4b43eb1e39fc0454ed8e9429aec12.jpg?1610505507\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.techbang.com%2Fsystem%2Fexcerpt_images%2F83780%2Fpost_inpage%2F9fd4b43eb1e39fc0454ed8e9429aec12.jpg%3F1610505507&h=23dd6dd3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nRazer 發布全新概念產品 Project Hazel，這個與醫學及科學家團隊合作的產品，標榜為全世界最智慧的口罩，以 N95 口罩為設計基礎，但可以重覆清潔後使用，在防護能力上可以過濾空氣中 95% 以上的危險顆粒，包括 COVID-19 病毒和其他常見病原體。<br />\n<br />\nRazer Project Hazel 以防水且耐刮擦的再生塑料製成，並以矽膠與臉部緊密貼合，可因個人臉形調整與塑型，也因為透明設計，因此，在與人交談時，可以看到嘴型與完整的臉部表情。此外，在 Project Hazel 的兩側設有主動式圓形通風裝置，主要的功能是用來使空氣流通，將呼出的二氧化碳排出，並且對吸入的空氣加以過濾，概念很像空氣清淨機。Razer 表示，這個主動式圓形通風裝置，可以過濾空氣中 95% 以上的危險顆粒，包括 COVID-19 病毒和其他常見病原體。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn0.techbang.com/system/images/583660/original/5da380e51b035ac728fd921d157d1cbe.jpg?1610508180\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn0.techbang.com%2Fsystem%2Fimages%2F583660%2Foriginal%2F5da380e51b035ac728fd921d157d1cbe.jpg%3F1610508180&h=4be9abb6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n此外，Project Hazel 也會配置麥克風、揚聲器，在與他人對話時，聲音能夠讓清晰傳達，且在口罩上還配有光感應器，當位於較暗的環境時，燈光就會自動亮起，讓他人可以看見自己，且可透過 Razer Chroma RGB 軟體來自定燈光顏色。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn1.techbang.com/system/images/583661/original/57dae9dfbe411352996fd0c2de6d27ec.jpg?1610508197\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn1.techbang.com%2Fsystem%2Fimages%2F583661%2Foriginal%2F57dae9dfbe411352996fd0c2de6d27ec.jpg%3F1610508197&h=ad5eb4c3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n除了 Project Hazel 外，也同步發表配置紫外線燈光的充電收納盒，只要將口罩放置於盒中，就可自動消毒附著在口罩上的細菌與病毒。不過，這個概念產品目前還沒有上市的相關資訊，仍屬於概念機，還未獲得食品和藥物管理局，疾病控制與預防中心或與健康管理局的任何必要批准和認證。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.techbang.com/system/images/583662/original/676708528a19d8bf2162f69f30b2f87a.jpg?1610508216\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.techbang.com%2Fsystem%2Fimages%2F583662%2Foriginal%2F676708528a19d8bf2162f69f30b2f87a.jpg%3F1610508216&h=832c913c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c53798581892cadcead5de10ab0bab6e8da869ee","tid":2366145,"uid":21886,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-14T09:25:49.000Z","msg":"我想要RGB燈效condom"},{"pid":"54f3563227d63c26b3937cd7489e1ad218d55579","tid":2366145,"uid":141837,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-14T09:27:09.000Z","msg":"股價返招股價先出聲啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d4ccac87f95a3ae855cb4a093e151a515e6ee8a","tid":2366145,"uid":77196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-14T09:27:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f3e486b9fe2695930e8719a83bca5629adc1a00","tid":2366145,"uid":241504,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-14T09:27:35.000Z","msg":"型"},{"pid":"3fea0c1aece7fce0417dc0a24b4b24515a76747b","tid":2366145,"uid":104138,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"c53798581892cadcead5de10ab0bab6e8da869ee","tid":2366145,"uid":21886,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-14T09:25:49.000Z","msg":"我想要RGB燈效condom"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-14T09:27:51.000Z","msg":"可以裝埋camera 第時有得第一人稱視角欣賞返"},{"pid":"89b954bd413a413947f032343a89a6b1cba3f98d","tid":2366145,"uid":126508,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-14T09:33:17.000Z","msg":"燈廠又不務正業啦"},{"pid":"c905e7b33e294509b41bced643ad7787dd68f8c8","tid":2366145,"uid":264683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-14T09:34:11.000Z","msg":"小型豬嘴<img src=\"/assets/faces/no